OL,3,CThe Metropolitan Police will resume
OL,4,Carresting Palestine Action protestors
OL,6,FThe Metropolitan Police has said it
OL,7,Fwill again begin arresting protestors
OL,8,Ffor holding signs in support of
OL,9,Fprescribed terror group, Palestine
OL,10,FAction.
OL,12,FThe force paused taking supporters
OL,13,Finto custody in February, after the
OL,14,FHigh Court ruled that the Government's
OL,15,Fban of the group was unlawful- this is
OL,16,Fnow being appealed.
OL,18,FLast night, the Met announced that
OL,19,Fofficers will be arresting protesters
OL,20,Fagain because the appeal is likely to
OL,21,Ftake several months.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/6
