OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1774530670
OL,3,CThe Metropolitan Police will resume
OL,4,Carresting Palestine Action protestors
OL,6,FDeputy Assistant Commissioner James
OL,7,FHarman said:
OL,9,F"While the High Court has found the
OL,10,Fproscription of Palestine Action to be
OL,11,Funlawful, it has confirmed the impact
OL,12,Fof that judgment will not take effect
OL,13,Funtil the Government's appeal has been
OL,14,Fconsidered which could take many
OL,15,Fmonths.
OL,17,F"That means it is still a criminal
OL,18,Foffence to support Palestine Action.
OL,26,@qD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/6
