CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1774530670
OL,3,CThe Metropolitan Police will resume
OL,4,Carresting Palestine Action protestors
OL,6,F"We must enforce the law as it is at
OL,7,Fthe time, not as it might be at a
OL,8,Ffuture date. We must do that
OL,9,Fconsistently and without fear or
OL,10,Ffavour."
OL,12,FHe continued: "The High Court decided
OL,13,Fon February 25 to grant the Home
OL,14,FSecretary permission to appeal and to
OL,15,Fleave the proscription in place
OL,16,Fpending the outcome of that appeal.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@HO]tD@OOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/6
