CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1774530670
OL,3,CThe Metropolitan Police will resume
OL,4,Carresting Palestine Action protestors
OL,6,F"Having now considered our position in
OL,7,Flight of that decision, taking into
OL,8,Faccount all the circumstances, we have
OL,9,Fdetermined that while Palestine Action
OL,10,Fremains proscribed and support for it
OL,11,Fremains unlawful under the Terrorism
OL,12,FAct.
OL,14,F"We must continue to enforce the law
OL,15,Fand this is likely to involve the
OL,16,Farrest of those committing offences."
OL,26,@nD@AOUxD@eO]
