OL,3,CThe Metropolitan Police will resume
OL,4,Carresting Palestine Action protestors
OL,6,FMore than 2,700 people have been
OL,7,Farrested so far for allegedly
OL,8,Fexpressing support for Palestine
OL,9,FAction since it was banned as a
OL,10,Fterrorist group last year.
OL,12,FProtesters have arranged mass rallies
OL,13,Fwhere demonstrators hold up signs
OL,14,Fsaying "I oppose genocide, I support
OL,15,FPalestine Action".
OL,17,FThe trials of hundreds of people
OL,18,Faccused of holding up the placards
OL,19,Fhave been put on hold while the legal
OL,20,Fbattle over whether the group should
OL,21,Fhave been banned rumbles on.
OL,26,@vD@HOUwD@QO]
